Ranger Help for: signal
=======================

SYNTAX:      signal <player> <message>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     1

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to send a short message to another player
through natural means - bird calls, wind patterns, and other nature
signals. The target player receives the message regardless of distance.
Only Rangers can send signals, but any player can receive them. The
extremely low SP cost reflects the simplicity of using natural phenomena
to carry messages. This is an in-character alternative to tells.
